// High rune Tier 2
Alias[RUNE_ALT_HIGH]: %BORDER-9B%%MAP-7D%%DOT-0B%%PURPLE%<%GREEN%!%PURPLE%> %NAME% %PURPLE%<%GREEN%!%PURPLE%>


// Magic Item 1 Affix
