//-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// GEMS
//-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// leveling gems
ItemDisplay[GEM~1-3 (FILTLVL=1 OR DIFF<2) FILTLVL<3]: %NAME%
// Hide low tier gems outside of normal or with filter strictness
